# WebBookRP API — requisições de exemplo (VS / VS Code REST Client)
# 1) Execute o login e copie o campo "token" da resposta para @token abaixo (ou use extensão que capture a resposta).
# 2) Perfis: http → localhost:5028 | https → https://localhost:7292

@WebBookRP_API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5028
@token = COLE_O_JWT_AQUI

@bookId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@serviceId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@postId = 1
@commentId = 1
@leadId = 1

###############################################################################
### Autenticação
###############################################################################

### Login — usuário da tabela Users (doc/insert.sql). Envie email ou username (e-mail).
POST {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

###

### Logout (stateless: cliente descarta o token)
POST {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/auth/logout

###

### Sessão — com token válido retorna authenticated: true
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/auth/session
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Sessão — sem token (anônimo)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/auth/session

###############################################################################
### Livros (A = Authorization)
###############################################################################

### Listar todos os livros (A)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/books
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Catálogo público (apenas ativos) (P)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/books/catalog
Accept: application/json

###

### Livro por id — público se ativo (P)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/books/{{bookId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar livro (A)
POST {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/books
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Exemplo de livro",
  "genre": "Ficção",
  "price": 49.90,
  "promoPrice": null,
  "active": true,
  "isPromotion": false,
  "cover": "",
  "synopsis": "Resumo curto",
  "coverSynopsis": null,
  "linkAmazon": null,
  "linkML": null,
  "linkShopee": null,
  "linkGeneric": null,
  "fullSynopsis": "<p>HTML opcional</p>",
  "pages": 200,
  "rating": 4.5,
  "reviews": 10
}

###

### Atualizar livro (A)
PUT {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/books/{{bookId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Exemplo atualizado",
  "genre": "Ficção",
  "price": 39.90,
  "promoPrice": 29.90,
  "active": true,
  "isPromotion": true,
  "cover": "",
  "synopsis": "Resumo",
  "coverSynopsis": null,
  "linkAmazon": null,
  "linkML": null,
  "linkShopee": null,
  "linkGeneric": null,
  "fullSynopsis": "<p>Conteúdo</p>",
  "pages": 200,
  "rating": 4.7,
  "reviews": 12
}

###

### Excluir livro (A)
DELETE {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/books/{{bookId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###############################################################################
### Serviços
###############################################################################

### Listar serviços ativos (P)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/services
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar todos (A)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/services/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Serviço por id (A)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/services/{{serviceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Criar serviço (A)
POST {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/services
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Consultoria",
  "price": 150.00,
  "unit": "hora",
  "active": true,
  "isPromotion": false,
  "promoPrice": null,
  "icon": "",
  "theme": "default",
  "description": "Descrição do serviço"
}

###

### Atualizar serviço (A)
PUT {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/services/{{serviceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Consultoria Plus",
  "price": 180.00,
  "unit": "hora",
  "active": true,
  "isPromotion": true,
  "promoPrice": 150.00,
  "icon": "",
  "theme": "default",
  "description": "Atualizado"
}

###

### Excluir serviço (A)
DELETE {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/services/{{serviceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###############################################################################
### Leads
###############################################################################

### Criar lead público (serviceId deve existir e estar ativo) (P)
POST {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "{{serviceId}}",
  "name": "Cliente Exemplo",
  "email": "cliente@exemplo.com",
  "phone": "11999999999",
  "description": "Quero mais informações"
}

###

### Listar leads com paginação e filtros (A)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/leads?page=1&pageSize=20&status=pending&search=
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Lead por id (A)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/leads/{{leadId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Atualizar status do lead (A)
PATCH {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/leads/{{leadId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "analyzing"
}

###

### Atualizar notas internas (A)
PATCH {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/leads/{{leadId}}/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Ligamos para o cliente em 10/04."
}

###

### Atualizar lead completo (A)
PUT {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/leads/{{leadId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serviceId": "{{serviceId}}",
  "name": "Cliente Exemplo",
  "email": "cliente@exemplo.com",
  "phone": "11999999999",
  "description": "Atualizado pelo painel",
  "value": 500.00,
  "status": "working",
  "notes": "Proposta enviada"
}

###

### Excluir lead (A)
DELETE {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/leads/{{leadId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###############################################################################
### Posts e comentários
###############################################################################

### Listar posts — anônimo: só published | autenticado: ?status=draft etc.
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts?status=published
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar posts (autenticado — ver rascunhos)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Post por id
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts/{{postId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar post (A)
POST {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Novo post",
  "category": "Geral",
  "coverType": "solid",
  "coverColor": "#1e293b",
  "coverText": "Título",
  "coverTextColor": "#ffffff",
  "imageUrl": null,
  "content": "Conteúdo em markdown ou texto",
  "externalLink": null,
  "allowLikes": true,
  "allowComments": true,
  "status": "draft"
}

###

### Atualizar post (A)
PUT {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Post atualizado",
  "category": "Geral",
  "coverType": "solid",
  "coverColor": "#1e293b",
  "coverText": "Título",
  "coverTextColor": "#ffffff",
  "imageUrl": null,
  "content": "Conteúdo",
  "externalLink": null,
  "allowLikes": true,
  "allowComments": true,
  "status": "published"
}

###

### Excluir post (A)
DELETE {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Alternar like (P) — por IP (post publicado e allowLikes)
POST {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts/{{postId}}/likes/toggle
Accept: application/json

###

### Comentar (P) — anônimo: informe guestName | logado: envie Authorization
POST {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Ótimo conteúdo!",
  "guestName": "Visitante"
}

###

### Marcar author-like no comentário (A)
PATCH {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments/{{commentId}}/author-like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "authorLike": true
}

###

### Excluir comentário (A)
DELETE {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###############################################################################
### Autor e configuração
###############################################################################

### Perfil do autor + timeline (P)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/author
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar autor + timeline (A)
PUT {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/author
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nome do Autor",
  "role": "Escritor",
  "avatarUrl": null,
  "secondaryImageUrl": null,
  "bio": "Biografia curta",
  "timeline": [
    {
      "id": null,
      "year": "2020",
      "title": "Marco",
      "description": "Descrição",
      "sortOrder": 0
    }
  ]
}

###

### Config sistema (A)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/config/system
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Config sistema — salvar JSON (A)
PUT {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/config/system
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": {
    "siteName": "WebBookRP",
    "contactEmail": "contato@exemplo.com"
  }
}

###

### Config home (A)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/config/home
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Config home — salvar JSON (A)
PUT {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/config/home
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": {
    "heroTitle": "Bem-vindo"
  }
}

###

### Estatísticas (StatsConfig) (A)
GET {{WebBookRP_API_HostAddress}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
